        "        ### Why a rule layer instead of running the model directly\n",
        "\n",
        "        The **LBNL XGBoost model** (Notebook 04, Test AUC 0.997) is trained on\n",
        "        **FCU-internal sensors**: cooling valve position, discharge airflow,\n",
